18 def gps_convert_ned(gps_t_lon, gps_t_lat,
19  gps_r_lon, gps_r_lat):
20  d_lon = gps_t_lon - gps_r_lon;
21  d_lat = gps_t_lat - gps_r_lat;
22  ned_x = (math.pi/180.)*d_lat * C_EARTH;
23  ned_y = (math.pi/180.)*d_lon * C_EARTH * math.cos((math.pi/180.)*gps_t_lat);
24  #s = 'ned_x: '+repr(ned_x) + ' ned_y: ' + repr(ned_y);
25  #print s;
26  return (ned_x, ned_y)
